OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some brightness. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be mainly
OL,8,Fdry and cloudy, a little light rain
OL,9,Fpossible across Orkney, perhaps
OL,10,Freaching Shetland by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy day with occasional
OL,13,Frain. Some brighter spells for Orkney
OL,14,Fin the afternoon, but also a few
OL,15,Fshowers possible. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
