OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Ffor most of Wednesday, wind and rain
OL,7,Flikely late evening. Early rain on
OL,8,FThursday clearing to a largely dry,
OL,9,Fbright and breezy day. Further rain on
OL,10,FFriday,
